subtitle: Accelerate Earnings with 3X GTA$ and RP on Open Wheel Races
content: Leave the laws of the road in your rearview and reap the benefits with Triple Rewards on Open Wheel Races. Choose your tires and time your visits to the pit lane in these high-speed races, handing out 3X GTA$ and RP all week long.
